igurations, themes and plugins we should test.'=>'通过允许我们追踪使用情况数据可更好地为您提供帮助，这可让我们知道应该用哪些WordPress配置、主题和插件进行测试。','Next message'=>'下一条消息','Dismiss this message'=>'关闭此消息','Previous message'=>'上一条消息','Plugin icon'=>'插件图标','General error'=>'一般错误','Error'=>'错误','DB tables'=>'数据库表','No DB tables found.'=>'为找到数据库表。','WP Mail SMTP DB tables are created'=>'WP Mail SMTP数据库表已创建','WP Mail SMTP DB tables check has failed'=>'WP Mail SMTP数据库表检查失败','Missing table: %s'=>'缺少数据库表: %s','Do WP Mail SMTP DB tables exist?'=>'WP Mail SMTP 数据库表是否存在?','WP Mail SMTP is using custom database tables for some of its features. In order to work properly, the custom tables should be created, and it looks like they exist in your database.'=>'WP Mail SMTP将自定义数据库表用于某些功能。 为了使其正常工作，请创建自定义表，检测到似乎这些表已存在于数据库中。','Warning icon'=>'警告图标','There was an error while upgrading the database. Please contact %1$s support with this information: %2$s.'=>'升级数据库时出错。 请联系%1$s支持并提供以下信息：%2$s。','Cancel'=>'取消','<p>The Default (PHP) mailer is currently selected, but is not recommended because in most cases it does not resolve email delivery issues.</p><p>Please consider selecting and configuring one of the other mailers.</p>'=>'<p>当前已选择“默认（PHP）”邮件程序，但由于大多数情况下它不能解决电子邮件传递问题，因此不建议这样做。</p><p>请考虑选择并配置其他邮件程序之一。</p>','Heads up!'=>'小心！','I already did'=>'已经完成','Yes'=>'是','We\'re sorry to hear you aren\'t enjoying WP Mail SMTP. We would love a chance to improve. Could you take a minute and let us know what we can do better?'=>'得知您不喜欢WP Mail SMTP，我们深感抱歉。 我们希望有一个改善的机会。 您能不能花一分钟让我们知道我们怎么做得更好吗？','Verify that the host\'s SSL certificate is valid.'=>'验证主机的SSL证书是否有效。','This means OpenSSL on your server isn\'t able to verify the host certificate.'=>'这意味着服务器上的OpenSSL无法验证主机证书。','They should be able to resolve this issue for you.'=>'他们应该能够为您解决此问题。','There is a known issue with PHP version 7.4.x, when using libpcre2 library version lower than 10.33.'=>'使用低于10.33的libpcre2库版本时，PHP 7.4.x版存在一个已知问题。','Your Sender Name option is incorrect.'=>'您的发件人姓名选项不正确。','There are a few reasons why this is happening. It could be that the host certificate is misconfigured, or this server\'s OpenSSL is using an outdated CA bundle.'=>'发生这种情况有几个原因。 可能是主机证书配置错误，或者该服务器的OpenSSL使用的是过时的CA捆绑软件。','Then click the “Allow plugin to send emails using your Google account” button and re-enable access.'=>'然后点击“允许插件使用您的Google帐户发送电子邮件”按钮，然后重新启用访问权限。','SMTP.com API Error.'=>'SMTP.com API错误。','Please re-grant Google app permissions!'=>'请重新授予Google应用权限！','Please make sure you entered an accurate Sender Name in WP Mail SMTP plugin settings.'=>'请确保您在WP Mail SMTP插件设置中输入了正确的发件人名称。','PCRE library issue'=>'PCRE库问题','No thanks'=>'不，谢谢','For a quick fix, until your web hosting resolves this, you can downgrade to PHP version 7.3 on your server.'=>'为了快速解决这个问题，在您的web主机解决这个问题之前，您可以将服务器降级为PHP 7.3版本。','(If cURL can\'t be enabled on your hosting server) Enable PHP setting: allow_url_fopen, by adding "allow_url_fopen = On" to the php.ini file (without the quotation marks)'=>'（如果无法在托管服务器上启用cURL）启用PHP设置：allow_url_fopen，方法是在php.ini文件中添加"allow_url_fopen = On"（不带引号）','(Recommended) Enable PHP extension: cURL, by adding "extension=curl" to the php.ini file (without the quotation marks) OR'=>'（推荐）启用PHP扩展：cURL，通过将"extension=curl"添加到php.ini文件中（不带引号）','Are you enjoying WP Mail SMTP?'=>'您喜欢WP Mail SMTP吗？','GuzzleHttp requires cURL, the allow_url_fopen ini setting, or a custom HTTP handler.'=>'GuzzleHttp需要cURL，allow_url_fopen ini设置或自定义HTTP处理程序。','If you don\'t know how to do the above we strongly suggest contacting your hosting support and provide them the "full Error Log for debugging" below and these steps. They should be able to fix this issue for you.'=>'如果您不知道如何执行上述操作，我们强烈建议您与主机支持联系，并在下面提供这些“调试的完整错误日志”以及这些步骤。 他们应该能够为您解决此问题。','It looks like your server is running PHP version 7.4.x with an outdated PCRE library (libpcre2) that has a known issue with email address validation.'=>'看来您的服务器运行的是带有过期PCRE库（libpcre2）的PHP 7.4.x版本，该库在电子邮件地址验证方面存在已知问题。','Misconfigured server certificate.'=>'服务器证书配置错误。','GuzzleHttp requirements.'=>'GuzzleHttp要求。','Contact your hosting support, show them the "full Error Log for debugging" below and share this <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">link</a> with them.'=>'请联系您的主机支持，向他们提供下面的 "用于调试的完整错误日志"，并附上<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">此链接</a>。','Please read this <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">support article</a> if you want to enable this option using constants.'=>'如果要通过常量启用此选项，请阅读此<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">支持文章</a>。','Edit your php.ini file on your hosting server.'=>'在您的虚拟主机上编辑php.ini文件。','Contact your web hosting provider and inform them you are having issues with libpcre2 library on PHP 7.4.'=>'请与您的web主机提供商联系，并告知他们您在PHP 7.4上的libpcre2库遇到问题。','If you\'d prefer not to set up SSL, or need an SMTP solution in the meantime, please select a different mailer option.'=>'如果您不想设置SSL或同时需要SMTP解决方案，请选择其他邮件程序选项。','%s requires an SSL certificate, and so is not currently compatible with your site. Please contact your host to request a SSL certificate, or check out <a href="https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-tutorials/how-to-add-ssl-and-https-in-wordpress/" target="_blank">WPBeginner\'s tutorial on how to set up SSL</a>.'=>'%s需要有效的SSL证书，因此您的网站无法使用此服务。请联系您的主机服务提供商要求安装SSL证书，或查看<a href="https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-tutorials/how-to-add-ssl-and-https-in-wordpress/" target="_blank">WPBeginner的教程，了解如何设置SSL</a>。','Learn More'=>'了解更多','Get Started with Pepipost'=>'开始使用Pepipost','Get Sender Name'=>'获取发件人名称','Follow this link to get a Sender Name from SMTP.com: %s.'=>'单击此链接可从SMTP.com获取发件人名称：%s。','Follow this link to get an API Key from SMTP.com: %s.'=>'单击此链接可从SMTP.com获取API密钥：%s。','SMTP.com'=>'SMTP.com','Get Started with SMTP.com'=>'开始使用SMTP.com','Get API Key'=>'获取API密钥','Sender Name'=>'发件人名称','Api Key:'=>'Api 密钥:','Go to WP Mail SMTP Settings page'=>'转至WP Mail SMTP设置页','Don\'t see what you\'re looking for?'=>'没找到你需要的？','Channel:'=>'频道：','Configure mailer'=>'配置邮件程序','The WP Mail SMTP plugin mailer setup is incomplete. Please click on the link below to access plugin settings and configure the mailer.'=>'WP Mail SMTP插件邮件程序配置尚未完成。 请单击下面的链接访问插件设置页面并配置邮件程序。','WP Mail SMTP mailer setup is incomplete'=>'WP Mail SMTP邮件程序尚未配置完成','You currently have the default mailer selected, which means that you haven’t set up SMTP yet.'=>'您当前选择的是默认邮件程序，这意味着您尚未设置SMTP。','Test email sending'=>'发送测试邮件','The WP Mail SMTP plugin mailer setup is complete. You can send a test email, to make sure it\'s working properly.'=>'WP Mail SMTP插件邮件程序配置已完成。 您可以发送一封测试邮件，以确保其可正常使用。','WP Mail SMTP mailer setup is complete'=>'WP Mail SMTP邮件程序配置已完成','Current mailer'=>'当前邮件程序','No debug notices found.'=>'暂无调试通知。','Debug'=>'调试','Is WP Mail SMTP mailer setup complete?'=>'WP Mail SMTP邮件程序是否配置完成？','Changes that you made to the settings are not saved!'=>'您对设置的更改尚未保存！','RafflePress Pro'=>'RafflePress Pro','License key type'=>'授权码类型','RafflePress'=>'RafflePress','WP Mail SMTP is brought to you by the same team that\'s behind the most user friendly WordPress forms, <a href="%1$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WPForms</a>, the largest WordPress resource site, <a href="%2$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WPBeginner</a>, the most popular lead-generation software, <a href="%3$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">OptinMonster</a>, the best WordPress analytics plugin, <a href="%4$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">MonsterInsights</a>, and <a href="%5$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">more</a>.'=>'WP Mail SMTP是由一个经验丰富的团队所开发，其产品包括最友好的WordPress表单插件<a href="%1$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WPForms</a>、最大的WordPress资源网站<a href="%2$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WPBeginner</a>、最受欢迎的潜在客户生成软件<a href="%3$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">OptinMonster</a>、最好的WordPress分析插件<a href="%4$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">MonsterInsights</a>和<a href="%5$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">更多</a>。','Pepipost SMTP'=>'Pepipost SMTP','Suggest a Mailer'=>'推荐邮件程序','Get the API Key'=>'获取 API 密钥','Read our <a href="%2$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Pepipost documentation</a> to learn how to configure Pepipost and improve your email deliverability.'=>'阅读我们的<a href="%2$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"> Pepipost文档</a>，以了解如何配置Pepipost并提高电子邮件的可达性。','<a href="%1$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Pepipost</a> is a transactional email service. Every month Pepipost delivers over 8 billion emails from 20,000+ customers. Their mission is to reliably send emails in the most efficient way and at the most disruptive pricing ever. Pepipost provides users 30,000 free emails the first 30 days.'=>'<a href="%1$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Pepipost</a>是一个付费的电子邮件服务。每个月Pepipost发送超过80亿封邮件，拥有2万多名客户。他们的任务是以最有效的方式、最具竞争力的价格提供可靠地电子邮件发送服务。Pepipost在前30天为用户提供3万封免费邮件额度。','Download'=>'下载','To send emails, change the value of the %1$s constant to %2$s.'=>'要发送电子邮件，请将%1$s常量的值更改为%2$s。','To send emails, go to plugin <a href="%s">Misc settings</a> and disable the "Do Not Send" option.'=>'要发送电子邮件，请到插件的<a href="%s">其他设置页面</a>，取消“停止发送邮件”选项。','We\'re sorry, the Microsoft Outlook mailer is not available on your plan. Please upgrade to the PRO plan to unlock all these awesome features.'=>'很抱歉，您使用的版本不支持Microsoft Outlook邮件功能。 请升级到PRO版本以解锁所有强大功能。','Amazon SES'=>'Amazon SES','We\'re sorry, the Amazon SES mailer is not available on your plan. Please upgrade to the PRO plan to unlock all these awesome features.'=>'很抱歉，您使用的版本不支持Amazon SES邮件功能。 请升级到PRO版本以解锁所有强大功能。','<strong>EMAILING DISABLED:</strong> The %s is currently blocking all emails from being sent.'=>'<strong>电子邮件已被禁止</strong>：%s禁止了所有电子邮件的发送。','Upgrade to Pro'=>'升级到专业版','Already purchased?'=>'已购买？','%name% is a PRO Feature'=>'%name% 为 Pro 版功能','<strong>Bonus:</strong> WP Mail SMTP users get <span>%s off</span> regular price,<br>applied at checkout.'=>'<strong>奖励：</strong>WP MAIL SMTP用户可获得<span>%s</span>的折扣，<br>并且在结账时会自动使用。','Hide Email Delivery Errors'=>'隐藏邮件发送错误','<strong>This is not recommended</strong> and should only be done for staging or development sites.'=>'<strong>不建议进行此操作</strong>，可以考虑在临时站点或开发站点中执行。','Email Delivery Errors were disabled using a %s filter.'=>'已使用%s禁用了电子邮件传递错误。','Educational notice for this mailer was successfully dismissed.'=>'此邮件的指导通知已成功撤销。','Get v3 API Key'=>'获取v3 API密钥','Follow this link to get an API Key: %s.'=>'请点击此链接获取API密钥: %s.','The Gmail mailer works well for sites that send low numbers of emails. However, Gmail\'s API has rate limitations and a number of additional restrictions that can lead to challenges during setup.<br><br>If you expect to send a high volume of emails, or if you find that your web host is not compatible with the Gmail API restrictions, then we recommend considering a different mailer option.'=>'Gmail邮件程序对于发送邮件数量较少的网站来说具有不错的效果体验，但Gmail的API在速率和设置方面均会有一些限制。<br><br>如果您需要发送大量的邮件，或发现您的WEB主机与Gmail API的限制不兼容，那么我们建议您考虑其他的邮件服务。','https://wpmailsmtp.com/'=>'https://wpmailsmtp.com/','Meanwhile you can switch to some other mailers.'=>'同时，您也可以改用其他的邮件程序。','There was an error while processing the Google authentication request. Please make sure that you have Client ID and Client Secret both valid and saved.'=>'处理Google身份验证请求时出错。 请确保您的客户端ID和客户端密钥都有效且已保存。','You have successfully linked the current site with your Google API project. Now you can start sending emails through Gmail.'=>'您已成功将当前站点与Google API项目相关联。 现在，您可以开始通过Gmail发送电子邮件。','Activate'=>'启用','Your site is running an <strong>insecure version</strong> of PHP that is no longer supported. Please contact your web hosting provider to update your PHP version or switch to a <a href="%1$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">recommended WordPress hosting company</a>.'=>'您的网站运行的是<strong>不安全的PHP版本</strong>，该版本不再受支持。 请与您的web主机服务提供商联系以更新您的PHP版本或更换到<a href="%1$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">我们推荐的WordPress主机服务商</a>。','<strong>WP Mail SMTP plugin is disabled</strong> on your site until you fix the issue. <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Read more for additional information.</a>'=>'您站点上的<strong> WP Mail SMTP插件已被禁用</strong>，直到您解决当前问题为止。  <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">详细了解更多信息。</a>','WP Mail SMTP Pro related message was successfully dismissed.'=>'WP Mail SMTP Pro相关消息已成功解除。','Could not install a plugin. Please download from WordPress.org and install manually.'=>'无法安装插件。 请从WordPress.org下载并手动安装。','Processing...'=>'处理中.....','Install and Activate'=>'安装并激活','License'=>'授权','License Key'=>'授权码','Your license key provides access to updates and support.'=>'您的授权码可以访问插件的更新和技术支持。','Additionally, you can take advantage of our White Glove Setup. Sit back and relax while we handle everything for you! If you simply don\'t have time or maybe you feel a bit in over your head - we got you covered.'=>'此外，您还可以利用我们的白手套设置。 在我们为您处理一切时，请坐下来放松一下！ 如果你根本没有时间，或者你觉得有点无法理解 - 我们让你满意。','To access our world class support, please <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">upgrade to WP Mail SMTP Pro</a>. Along with getting expert support, you will also get Notification controls, Email Logging, and integrations for Amazon SES, Office 365, and Outlook.com.'=>'如需得到我们全球的技术支持，请<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">升级至 WP Mail SMTP Pro</a>。除了可以获得专业技术支持外，还可以使用通知控制项、电子邮件记录，以及整合 Amazon SES、Office 365、Outlook.com 电子邮件服务等多项功能。','As a valued WP Mail SMTP user, you will get <span class="price-off">%s off regular pricing</span>, automatically applied at checkout!'=>'作为一名有价值的WP Mail SMTP用户，您将获得<span class="price-off">%s</span>的折扣，并在结账时自动使用！','Customer Support'=>'客户支持','Email Controls'=>'电邮控制','Emails are not logged'=>'电子邮件未记录','Feature'=>'特点','Get the most out of WP Mail SMTP by upgrading to Pro and unlocking all of the powerful features.'=>'通过升级到Pro并解锁所有强大功能，充分利用WP Mail SMTP。','Plugin installed.'=>'已安装插件。','Plugin installed & activated.'=>'已安装并激活插件。','Could not install the plugin.'=>'无法安装插件。','Plugin activated.'=>'插件已激活。','Could not activate the plugin. Please activate it from the Plugins page.'=>'无法激活插件。 请从“插件”页面激活它。','WPForms Pro'=>'WPForms Pro (专业版)','Priority Support'=>'优先支持','Limited Support'=>'有限支持','MonsterInsights Pro'=>'MonsterInsights Pro','OptinMonster'=>'OptinMonster','Pro'=>'Pro(专业版)','Check your inbox you used to create a Mailgun account. Click the activation link in an email from Mailgun.'=>'检查您用于创建Mailgun帐户的收件箱。 单击Mailgun电子邮件中的激活链接。','It seems that you forgot to activate your Mailgun account.'=>'您似乎忘了激活您的Mailgun帐户。','Enter email address where test email will be sent.'=>'输入将发送测试电子邮件的电子邮件地址。','Get WP Mail SMTP Pro Today and Unlock all of these Powerful Features'=>'立即获取WP Mail SMTP Pro并解锁所有这些强大的功能','Inactive'=>'未启用','MonsterInsights'=>'MonsterInsights','Status: %s'=>'状态： %s','The WPForms Team'=>'WPForms团队','The WPForms Team photo'=>'WPForms团队照片','If you do not see activation email, go to your Mailgun control panel and resend the activation email.'=>'如果您没有看到激活电子邮件，请转到您的Mailgun控制面板并重新发送激活电子邮件。','Complete Email Controls management for most default WordPress emails'=>'完成大多数默认WordPress电子邮件的电子邮件控件管理','No controls over whether default WordPress emails are sent'=>'对 WordPress 的默认电子邮件发送不提供管理控制项','Yup, we know a thing or two about building awesome products that customers love.'=>'是的，我们知道如何打造客户喜爱的优秀产品。','Contact Forms by WPForms'=>'Contact Forms by WPForms','Bonus: WP Mail SMTP Lite users get <span class="price-off">%s off regular price</span>, automatically applied at checkout.'=>'奖励：WP MAIL SMTP基本版用户可获得<span class="price-off">%s的折扣</span>，并在结账时会自动使用。','Our goal is to make reliable email deliverability easy for WordPress.'=>'我们的目标是为WordPress提供可靠的电子邮件传送功能。','Email deliverability has been a well-documented problem for all WordPress websites. However as WPForms grew, we became more aware of this painful issue that affects our users and the larger WordPress community. So we decided to solve this problem and make a solution that\'s beginner friendly.'=>'对于大多WordPress站点，电子邮件的可达性是一个众所周知的问题。随着WPForms的发展，我们见见意识到了这个影响我们用户和广大WordPress社区的困难问题。所以我们决定将其解决并做出一套对初学者友好的解决方案。','About Us'=>'关于我们','Connected as %s'=>'连接到%s','%s vs Pro'=>'%s vs Pro','Email Log'=>'电子邮件日志','You need to save settings with Client ID and Client Secret before you can proceed.'=>'您需要先使用客户端ID和客户端密钥保存设置，然后才能继续。','%1$s \\a\\t %2$s'=>'%1$s \\a\\t %2$s','Upgrade to WP Mail SMTP Pro'=>'升级到WP Mail SMTP Pro','Hello and welcome to WP Mail SMTP, the easiest and most popular WordPress SMTP plugin. We build software that helps your site reliably deliver emails every time.'=>'您好，欢迎使用WP MAIL SMTP，简单且受欢迎的WordPress SMTP插件。我们打造的软件可让您的站点每次都能稳定地进行邮件的发送。','Please copy this URL into the "Authorized redirect URIs" field of your Google web application.'=>'请将此URL复制到您的Google Web应用的 "授权重定向URI "字段中。','All the defined constants will stop working and you will be able to change all the values on this page.'=>'所有定义的常量将停止工作，您将能够更改此页面上的所有值。','If you want to disable the use of constants, find in %1$s file the constant %2$s and turn if off:'=>'如果要禁用常量，请在%1$s文件中找到常量%2$s并关闭：','To change the password you need to change the value of the constant there: %s'=>'要更改密码，您需要更改常量的值：%s','The value of this field was set using a constant %1$s most likely inside %2$s of your WordPress installation.'=>'此字段的值是使用常量%1$s设置的，最有可能在WordPress安装的%2$s内。','Please deactivate the free version of the WP Mail SMTP plugin before activating WP Mail SMTP Pro.'=>'请在激活WP Mail SMTP Pro之前禁用免费版的WP Mail SMTP插件。','Pepipost'=>'Pepipost','Click the button above to confirm authorization.'=>'按一下上方按钮以确认授权。','Authorization'=>'验证','Copy URL to clipboard'=>'复制网址至剪贴板','Client ID'=>'客户端 ID','%1$s requires PHP %2$s to work and does not support your current PHP version %3$s. Please contact your host and request a PHP upgrade to the latest one.'=>'%1$s 需要 PHP %2$s (或更新版本) 才能正确执行，它不支持这台主机目前所使用的 PHP %3$s。请联系您的主机服务商，并提出将 PHP 升级至最新版的要求。','SMTP Password'=>'SMTP 密码','Auto TLS'=>'自动 TLS','TLS'=>'TLS','SSL'=>'SSL','None'=>'无','<a href="%s" rel="" target="_blank">More information</a> on Mailgun.com.'=>'请参考 Mailgun.com 上的<a href="%s" rel="" target="_blank">进一步说明</a>。','Define which endpoint you want to use for sending messages.'=>'请选取要用于发送信息的端点。','EU'=>'欧盟','US'=>'美国','Region'=>'发件/资料储存地区','Get a Domain Name'=>'取得域名','Follow this link to get a Domain Name from Mailgun: %s.'=>'请依照《%s》(英文) 中的指示，从 Mailgun 取得域名。','Domain Name'=>'域名','Private API Key'=>'私有 API 密钥','Mailgun'=>'Mailgun','API Key'=>'API 密钥','SendGrid'=>'SendGrid','Other SMTP'=>'其他 SMTP','Recommended next steps:'=>'建议的处理步骤:','An issue was detected.'=>'检测出问题。','Make sure that the generated email has a TO header, useful when you are responsible for email creation.'=>'确认产生的电子邮件具备 TO (收件人) 标头，这对负责建立电子邮件的人员会非常有帮助。','Check the "Send To" email address used and confirm it is a valid email and was not empty.'=>'检查输入于 [收件人] 栏位的电子邮件地址，并确认它是有效的电子邮件地址且非空值。','Please click "Agree", if you see that button. If not - you will need to enable less secure apps first:'=>'如果有 [允许] 按钮，请点击该按钮；如果并未出现该按钮，必须先启用低安全性应用程序:','Google API Error.'=>'Google API 发生错误。','Complete the steps in section "2. Verify Your Domain".'=>'请完成《2. 验证域名》(英文) 章节中的步骤。','Your Mailgun account does not have access to send emails.'=>'目前的 Mailgun 帐号没有发送电子邮件的权限。','Mailgun failed.'=>'存取 Mailgun 发生错误。','no'=>'不','Your SMTP host is rejecting the connection.'=>'SMTP 服务器拒绝连接。','Your web server is blocking the connection.'=>'目前的网站服务器阻止了发送至 SMTP 服务器的连接。','Could not connect to the SMTP host.'=>'无法连接至 SMTP 服务器。','Enable Authentication'=>'启用验证','Unauthenticated senders are not allowed.'=>'不接受未验证的发件人。','Verify with them your SMTP account is in good standing and your account has not been flagged.'=>'请联系 SMTP 服务供应商，确认目前的 SMTP 帐号是否仍具备使用资格，以及帐号是否已遭标帜。','Contact your SMTP host to ask about sending/rate limits.'=>'请联系 SMTP 服务供应商洽询关于电子邮件发送配额限制的相关资讯。','This means the connection to your SMTP host was made successfully, but the host rejected the email.'=>'这代表可成功连接至 SMTP 服务器，但 SMTP 服务器拒绝发送邮件。','Error due to unsolicited and/or bulk e-mail.'=>'由于来路不明电子邮件及/或大量电子邮件导致发生错误。','Verify with your SMTP host that your account has permissions to send emails using outside connections.'=>'请联系 SMTP 服务供应商，确认目前使用的帐号是否具备以外部连接发送电子邮件的权限。','Could not authenticate your SMTP account.'=>'无法验证 SMTP 帐号。','Contact your web hosting provider and inform them you are having issues making outbound connections.'=>'联系这个网站的主机服务供应商，并通知它网站主机在进行外寄连接时发生问题。','Could not connect to your host.'=>'无法连接至 SMTP 服务器。','Contact your web hosting provider and ask them to verify your server can connect to %s. Additionally, ask them if a firewall or security policy may be preventing the connection.'=>'联系这个网站的主机服务供应商，并要求它确认网站服务器是否连接至 %s。此外，同时询问它是否有防火墙或安全性原则禁止了相关连接。','Typically this error is returned your web server is blocking the connections or the SMTP host denying the request.'=>'一般来说，传回这项错误是因为这个网站的服务器阻止了发送至 SMTP 服务器的连接或 SMTP 服务器拒绝了连接要求。','This means your web server was unable to connect to the host server.'=>'这代表这个网站的服务器无法连接至 SMTP 服务器。','This means your web server was unable to connect to %s.'=>'这代表这个网站的服务器无法连接至 %s。','Could not connect to host.'=>'无法连接至 SMTP 服务器。','Ask them to resolve the issue then try again.'=>'要求它解决问题然后再试一次。','The exact error you can provide them is in the Error log, available at the bottom of this page.'=>'请提供错误记录中的确切错误，这些资讯可于本页底部找到。','Contact your web hosting provider and inform them your site has an issue with SSL certificates.'=>'联系这个网站的主机服务供应商，并通知它这个网站有 SSL 凭证的问题。','This means your web server cannot reliably make secure connections (make requests to HTTPS sites).'=>'这代表这个网站的服务器无法可靠地建立安全连接 (向 HTTPS 网站发出要求)。','SSL certificate issue.'=>'SSL 凭证问题。','Test email to %s'=>'发送至 %s 的测试电子邮件','Test failed. Please use a valid email address and try to resend the test email.'=>'测试失败。请输入有效的电子邮件地址并重新发送测试电子邮件。','Send Email'=>'发送电子邮件','Off'=>'停用','On'=>'启用','HTML'=>'HTML 格式电子邮件','Send To'=>'收件人','Uninstall WP Mail SMTP'=>'解除安装 WP Mail SMTP','Hide Announcements'=>'隐藏通知','You will need to consult with their documentation to switch them to use default WordPress email delivery.'=>'网站管理员需要查阅这类插件的相关说明文件，将其切换为使用预设的 WordPress 电子邮件发送方式。','Do Not Send'=>'停止发送邮件','General'=>'一般','Misc'=>'其他','WPForms'=>'WPForms','Allow plugin to send emails using your Google account'=>'授与插件使用您的 Google 帐户发送电子邮件的权限','Authorized redirect URI'=>'已授权的重定向 URI','SMTP Username'=>'SMTP用户名','For most servers TLS is the recommended option. If your SMTP provider offers both SSL and TLS options, we recommend using TLS.'=>'对于大多数服务器，建议使用TLS。 如果您的SMTP提供商同时提供SSL和TLS选项，我们建议您使用TLS。','If you are operating under EU laws, you may be required to use EU region.'=>'如果您在欧盟法律下运营，您可能需要使用欧盟地区。','Default (none)'=>'默认（无）','To send emails you will need only a %s access level for this API key.'=>'要发送电子邮件，您只需要%s访问级别即可获得此API密钥。','Create API Key'=>'创建API密钥','Need support?'=>'需要技术支持？','Try using a different mailer.'=>'尝试使用其他邮件程序。','Your host is rejecting the connection.'=>'您的SMTP主机拒绝连接。','Plugin settings are incorrect (wrong SMTP settings, invalid Mailer configuration, etc).'=>'插件设置不正确，例如错误的 SMTP 设置、不正确的邮件程序设置等。','Try to use a separate project for your emails, so the project has only 1 Gmail API in it enabled. You will need to remove the old project and create a new one from scratch.'=>'尝试为您的电子邮件使用单独的项目，因此该项目只启用了1个Gmail API。 您需要删除旧项目并从头开始创建一个新项目。','You may have added a new API to a project'=>'您可能已向项目添加了新API','Thanks for using WP Mail SMTP! To complete the plugin setup and start sending emails, <strong>please select and configure your <a href="%s">Mailer</a></strong>.'=>'感谢采用 WP Mail SMTP。要完成插件设置并开始发送电子邮件，<strong>请先选取<a href="%s">邮件程序</a>并加以配置</strong>。','Force From Name'=>'强制使用 [发件人名称] 设置','If checked, the From Email setting above will be used for all emails, ignoring values set by other plugins.'=>'启用这项设置后，上方 [发件人电子邮件地址] 中的设置便会套用至全部外寄电子邮件，并忽略其他插件的相关设置。','Force From Email'=>'强制使用 [发件人电子邮件地址] 设置','Please note that other plugins can change this, to prevent this use the setting below.'=>'请注意，其他插件能变更这项设置值；如需防止变更，请使用下方的设置。','Reinstall the plugin with clean plugin data turned on on Misc page. This will remove all the plugin options and you will be safe to retry.'=>'在 [其他] 分页中启用清除插件资料重新安装插件的设置。这会删除全部插件设置资料，以便进行重新设置。','Make sure that you are not trying to manually clean up the plugin options to retry the "Allow..." step.'=>'确认未曾尝试手动清除插件设置，以便重试 [允许] 步骤。','Go to plugin Settings page and click the "Allow plugin to send emails using your Google account" button.'=>'前往插件设置页面并点击 [授与插件使用 Google 帐户发送电子邮件的权限] 按钮。','Make sure that you have clicked the "Allow plugin to send emails using your Google account" button under Gmail settings.'=>'确认在插件的 Gmail 设置中已点击过 [授与插件使用 Google 帐户发送电子邮件的权限] 按钮。','You have not properly configured Gmail mailer.'=>'这代表 Gmail 邮件程序目前并未正确配置。','Go to our how-to guide for setting up <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Mailgun with WP Mail SMTP</a>.'=>'请参阅这篇《<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">如何使用 WP Mail SMTP 插件以 Mailgun 为 WordPress 网站发送电子邮件 </a>》(英文) 以进行必要的设置。','Triple check your SMTP settings including host address, email, and password, port, and security.'=>'请反复检查 SMTP 相关设置是否正确，包含 SMTP 服务器地址、发件帐号及密码、通讯埠及安全性设定。','SMTP settings are incorrect (wrong port, security setting, incorrect host).'=>'SMTP 的相关设置不正确，例如错误的通讯埠号、安全性设置有误或不正确的 SMTP 服务器地址。','Go to WP Mail SMTP plugin Settings page.'=>'前往 WP Mail SMTP 插件 [设置] 页面。','This means the connection to your SMTP host was made successfully, but you should enable Authentication and provide correct Username and Password.'=>'这代表可成功连接至 SMTP 服务器，但必须启用插件的中的 [验证] 设置并提供正确的 [STMP 使用者名称] 及 [SMTP 密码]。','Triple check your SMTP settings including host address, email, and password. If you have recently reset your password you will need to update the settings.'=>'请反复检查 SMTP 相关设置是否正确，包含 SMTP 服务器地址、发件帐号及密码。如果最近变更过发件密码，请更新插件中的相关设置。','Typically this error is returned when the email or password is not correct or is not what the SMTP host is expecting.'=>'一般来说，传回这项错误是因为设置了不正确的发件帐号/密码或设置不符合 SMTP 服务器规则。','This means we were able to connect to your SMTP host, but were not able to proceed using the email/password in the settings.'=>'这代表插件能够连接至指定的 SMTP 服务器，但无法以设置中的电子邮件地址 (帐号)/密码继续执行。','If using "Other SMTP" Mailer, contact your SMTP host to confirm they are accepting outside connections with the settings you have configured (address, username, port, security, etc).'=>'如果使用了 [其他 SMTP] 邮件程序，请联系 SMTP 服务供应商以确认 SMTP 服务器是否接受包含目前设置 (SMTP 服务器地址、使用者名称、通讯埠、安全性设置等等) 的外部连接。','If using "Other SMTP" Mailer, triple check your SMTP settings including host address, email, and password.'=>'如果使用了 [其他 SMTP] 邮件程序，请反复检查 SMTP 相关设置是否正确，包含 SMTP 服务器地址、发件帐号及密码。','Typically this error is returned when web server is not configured properly.'=>'一般来说，传回这项错误是因为网页服务器并未正确配置。','You cannot send an email. Mailer is not properly configured. Please check your settings.'=>'由于邮件程序并未正确设定，因此这个网站无法发送电子邮件。请检查相关设置。','Send this email in HTML or in plain text format.'=>'设置要以 HTML 或纯文字格式发送测试电子邮件。','Test emails are allowed to be sent, regardless of this option.'=>'无论这项设置为何，插件都会发送测试电子邮件。','Enter correct SMTP Username (usually this is an email address) and Password in the appropriate fields.'=>'在对应的栏位输入正确的 SMTP 用户名 (通常就是电子邮件地址) 及密码。','Contact your SMTP host to confirm you are using the correct username and password.'=>'请联系 SMTP 服务供应商，确认目前使用的用户名及密码是否正确。','Activated'=>'已启用(Activated)','Not Installed'=>'未安装','Install Plugin'=>'安装插件','As a WP Mail SMTP Pro user you have access to WP Mail SMTP priority support. Please log in to your WPMailSMTP.com account and <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">submit a support ticket</a>.'=>'作为WP Mail SMTP Pro用户，您可以访问WP Mail SMTP获得优先支持。 请登录您的WPMailSMTP.com帐户并<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">提交支持服务单</a>。','Please rate <strong>WP Mail SMTP</strong> <a href="%1$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</a> on <a href="%2$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WordPress.org</a> to help us spread the word. Thank you from the WP Mail SMTP team!'=>'请评价<strong>WP Mail SMTP</strong> <a href="%1$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</a> 在 <a href="%2$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WordPress.org</a>来帮助我们推广。 WP Mail SMTP团队向您致敬！','Save Settings'=>'保存设置','Settings were successfully saved.'=>'设置已成功保存。','Some plugins, like BuddyPress and Events Manager, are using their own email delivery solutions. By default, this option does not block their emails, as those plugins do not use default <code>wp_mail()</code> function to send emails.'=>'某些插件 (如 BuddyPress 及 Events Manager) 会采用自有的电子邮件发送解决方案。依照预设，这项设置不会阻止这类插件发送电子邮件，因为他们并不是使用预设的 <code>wp_mail()</code> 函数发送电子邮件。','Version'=>'版本','Alternatively, we also offer <a href="%1$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">limited support</a> on the WordPress.org support forums. You can <a href="%2$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">create a support thread</a> there, but please understand that free support is not guaranteed and is limited to simple issues. If you have an urgent or complex issue, then please consider <a href="%3$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">upgrading to WP Mail SMTP Pro</a> to access our priority support ticket system.'=>'另外，我们也在WordPress.org支持论坛上提供<a href="%1$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">基本的技术支持</a>。您可以在此处<a href="%2$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">创建支持单</a>，但是请理解，基本技术支持仅限于简单的问题。如果您有紧急或复杂的问题，请考虑<a href="%3$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">升级到WP Mail SMTP Pro </a>以获取我们的优先支持服务。','Client Secret'=>'客户端密钥','Typically this error is returned when you are sending too many e-mails or e-mails that have been identified as spam.'=>'通常，当发送过多的邮件或邮件被识别为垃圾邮件时，会返回此错误。','Active'=>'激活','Are you sure you want to reset the current provider connection? You will need to immediately create a new one to be able to send emails.'=>'您是否要重置当前的邮件程序连接？ 注意，重置之后，您需要创建新的程序连接才能够发送电子邮件。','Typically this error is returned for one of the following reasons:'=>'通常，返回此错误是因为以下原因之一而导致：','Contact your web hosting provider and ask them to verify your server can connect to %1$s on port %2$s using %3$s encryption. Additionally, ask them if a firewall or security policy may be preventing the connection - many shared hosts block certain ports.<br><strong>Note: this is the most common cause of this issue.</strong>'=>'请与您的web主机服务商联系，并让他们验证服务器是否可以使用%3$s加密连接至%1$s的%2$s端口。 此外，请询问他们防火墙或安全策略是否阻止了连接-许多虚拟主机可能会阻止连接某些端口。<br> <strong>注意：这是此问题最常见的原因。</strong>','After the click you should be redirected to a Gmail authorization screen, where you will be asked a permission to send emails on your behalf.'=>'点击后，会重定向到Gmail的授权页面，在此页面中，插件会要求授权使用当前账户发送邮件的权限。','if you are using regular Gmail account, please <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">read this article</a> to proceed.'=>'如果您使用的是普通Gmail账户，请<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">阅读本文</a>以继续进行。','If you\'re using an email provider (Yahoo, Outlook.com, etc) this should be your email address for that account.'=>'如果你使用的电子邮件服务是（雅虎、Outlook.com等），啧地址应该是这些服务账户的电子邮件地址。','There was an error while processing the authentication request. Please make sure that you have Client ID and Client Secret both valid and saved.'=>'处理身份验证请求时出错。 请确认您的客户端ID和客户端密钥有效并已经保存。','Please review your WP Mail SMTP settings in <a href="%s">plugin admin area</a>.'=>'请在<a href="%s">插件管理页面</a>中查看您的WP MAIL SMTP设置。','Follow this link to get an API Key from SendGrid: %s.'=>'请按照此链接的说明从SendGrid获取API密钥：%s。','Email Test'=>'电邮测试','Dismiss this notice'=>'忽略此通知','Please <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">read this article</a> to learn more about what can cause this error and follow the steps below.'=>'请 <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">阅读本文</a>，了解更多可能导致此错误的原因，并遵循以下步骤。','You have successfully linked the current site with your Zoho Mail API project. Now you can start sending emails through Zoho Mail.'=>'您已成功将当前站点与您的Zoho Mail API项目链接。现在您可以开始通过Zoho Mail发送邮件了。','The email address that emails are sent from.'=>'用于发出邮件的电邮地址。','If unchecked, bounce messages may be lost.'=>'如未选中此复选框，退回的邮件可能会丢失。','By default, TLS encryption is automatically used if the server supports it (recommended). In some cases, due to server misconfigurations, this can cause issues and may need to be disabled.'=>'默认情况下，如果服务器支持TLS加密，则会自动使用TLS加密（推荐）。在某些情况下，由于服务器配置错误可能会导致问题，则需要将其禁用。','The name that emails are sent from.'=>'发出邮件的发件人名称。','Install'=>'安装','There was an error while processing the authentication request. Please try again.'=>'处理身份验证请求时发生错误。请重试。','There was an error while processing the authentication request: %s. Please try again.'=>'处理身份验证请求时发生错误：%s。请重试。','Return Path indicates where non-delivery receipts - or bounce messages - are to be sent.'=>'返回路径会指示未送达回执（或退回邮件）将被发送到何处。','If checked, the From Name setting above will be used for all emails, ignoring values set by other plugins.'=>'如果勾选此复选框，上面设置的发件人名称将会用于所有邮件，并忽略其他插件设置的值。','WP Mail SMTP is a free plugin, and the team behind WPForms maintains it to give back to the WordPress community.'=>'WP Mail SMTP是一个免费插件，由WPForms背后的团队对其进行维护并回报给WordPress社区。','There was a problem while sending the test email.'=>'发送测试邮件时出现问题。','Contact your web hosting provider and ask them to verify your server can make outside connections. Additionally, ask them if a firewall or security policy may be preventing the connection - many shared hosts block certain ports.<br><strong>Note: this is the most common cause of this issue.</strong>'=>'联系您的虚拟主机提供商，请他们验证您的服务器是否可以进行外部连接。此外，请询问他们是否有防火墙或安全策略会阻止连接 - 许多共享主机会阻止某些端口。<br><strong>注：这是导致此问题的最常见原因。</strong>','This means your test email was unable to be sent.'=>'这意味着您的测试邮件无法发送。','Please follow our <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Gmail tutorial</a> to be sure that all the correct project and data is applied.'=>'请遵循我们的<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Gmail教程</a>，以确保所有项目和数据被正确应用。','Make sure that the used Client ID/Secret correspond to a proper project that has Gmail API enabled.'=>'确保所使用的客户端ID/密钥正确对应于已启用Gmail API的项目。','Make sure that you have Gmail API enabled, and you can do that <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">here</a>.'=>'请确保您已启用了Gmail API，您可在<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">这里</a>进行操作。','There are various reasons for that, please review the steps below.'=>'有许多原因会造成此情况，请查看以下步骤。','Make sure there is no aggressive caching on site admin area pages or try to clean cache between attempts.'=>'确认站点管理区页面未采用增强缓存，或在每次尝试连接后清除缓存。','Authentication code that Google returned to you has already been used on your previous auth attempt.'=>'Google返回的身份验证代码已在您之前的身份验证尝试中使用。','Unfortunately, this error can be due to many different reasons.'=>'不过，此错误通常由许多不同原因造成。','It should be something like this: %1$s. These are incorrect values: %2$s.'=>'正确的值：%1$s。不正确的值：%2$s。','Save Changes'=>'保存更改','Settings'=>'设置','Authentication'=>'认证','Encryption'=>'加密','SMTP Port'=>'SMTP 端口','SMTP Host'=>'SMTP 主机','From Name'=>'发件人名称','From Email'=>'发件人','Return Path'=>'返回路径','WP Mail SMTP'=>'WP Mail SMTP','Mailer'=>'邮件程序','Send a Test Email'=>'发送测试邮件']];